Tyrael: Kaiser, I'm taking command. Take Blackheart in a CR chamber
and put him in cryosleep. After that, find me a blank protoform.

He enters the base by a secondary door and leaves the stasis pod on
the floor.

Tyrael: There, join us when you're ready... I'll be busy with the next
step.
